data.description:
VA Assumable 3.75% Loan 

Strategically nestled just 45 minutes from the vibrant heart of downtown Denver, this exquisite 4bd/2bth gem is a dream come true for those seeking a harmonious blend of comfort and convenience. Located a brisk 20-minute drive from Buckley AFB and a mere 15 minutes from the airport, this home truly bridges the best of both worlds.

Step inside to be greeted by a luminous open main floor that radiates warmth and charm. The heart of the home – the kitchen – is both practical and picturesque, showcasing newer appliances, a large pantry, and ample counter space that would delight any culinary enthusiast. This flows effortlessly into a living area designed for making memories.

The property boasts a vast backyard that is an entertainer's delight, ready to be used to enjoy those serene summer evenings. The oversized 2-car garage is not just a haven for your vehicles but also promises additional alley parking, ensuring your guests are always catered for.

The intelligently designed main floor offers a versatile guest room, ideal for visitors or as a dedicated home office – perfect for today's work-from-home era. Furthermore, the convenience of an on-floor bathroom is an added luxury.

Ascend to the upper level and discover a sanctuary of relaxation. The primary suite serves as a personal retreat, while two additional spacious bedrooms await. Functionality is at its peak with a dedicated laundry room, making chores a breeze.

But this home's charm doesn't end within its walls. Step outside to the covered front porch, and you're immediately greeted by the picturesque view of the neighborhood. It’s a constant reminder of the community spirit that's alive and thriving.

Your dining and shopping needs? Consider them covered. Restaurants and major shopping outlets are just around the corner, and with swift access to I70, the broader Denver area is always within reach.
